channel.title: Do you know who noobs remind me of?
channel.description:
Shinji Ikari.
Quote from end of evangelion, the bit with Asuka, "help me, please, somebody help me!"
I can get more but it's mostly along the lines of "help me, please, somebody help me!" and can't be asked to look through all 26 episodes quickly. O_o

[quote=“frank_, post:5, topic:12543”]i dono…shinji is more like harry potter

noobs are just idiots[/quote]

Yeah, suppose so. Shinji just goes mentally unstable(hey, who wouldn’t after watching evangelion straght for 6 hours into the early hours of the morning) in the last few episodes. Rei still owns Shinji though.
